  <bioghist id="aspace_3fc04514a83093b5c56ce37750bd7636">
    <head>Biographical Note - John Cromwell Holtz</head>
<p>John Holtz was the founder and director of the International Contemporary Organ Music Festival from 1971-1984.[Source: "Holtz, John Cromwell," Hartford Courant, October 31, 2001.]</p>  </bioghist>
