  <scopecontent id="aspace_bb61ba572c4c9bbd73bb839943c3d48f">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection consists primarily of printed music and scores, and in some cases synopses, texts, and instructions, and correspondence regarding organ compositions and performances. Many of these compositions were composed and/or performed for the International Contemporary Organ Music Festival. The collection also contains programs from Holtz's performances, scrapbooks and publicity materials of his career and the organ festival, as well as notes, writings, and other various papers.</p>  </scopecontent>
