  <dsc><c01 id="aspace_97f8d41bebf5388451de4869b39cba67" level="file"><did><unittitle>Compositions</unittitle><physdesc altrender="part"><extent altrender="materialtype spaceoccupied">9 Folders</extent><dimensions>legal size</dimensions></physdesc><physdesc altrender="part"><extent altrender="materialtype spaceoccupied">1 Folders</extent><dimensions>20 x 24" oversize</dimensions></physdesc><physdesc altrender="part"><extent altrender="materialtype spaceoccupied">4 Folders</extent><dimensions>13 x 18" oversize</dimensions></physdesc><unitdate normal="1963/1982" type="inclusive">1963-1982, undated</unitdate><container altrender="document box legal (D15105)" id="aspace_0a6d27d43d5b1f1c03701fc0ef6a3f25" label="Mixed Materials [0207303179916]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_b88a3c08ac8b062e0698ba7e599fba83" parent="aspace_0a6d27d43d5b1f1c03701fc0ef6a3f25" type="folder">1-9</container><container altrender="oversize drop front 20 x 24 thin (PB24201)" id="aspace_e0b477c683e53e486f2ad690f55154ec" label="Notated Music [0207303178090]" type="box">Shared Oversized 2</container><container id="aspace_b7dced3bd6ed3cd59d02f8b0561271f6" parent="aspace_e0b477c683e53e486f2ad690f55154ec" type="folder">OV 1 (Gmeeoorh)</container><container id="aspace_738249bf311eda6c9c716659b3802c37" label="Notated Music [0207303179130]" type="folder">OV folder 3</container><container altrender="oversized 18x13 dropfront (DFBG1813)" id="aspace_13ba7b487187439c0b61d66165d8e8bf" label="Notated Music [0207303177159]" type="box">Shared Small Oversized 2</container><container id="aspace_050d1d5baa9820a08a08c1c79acf0b8c" parent="aspace_13ba7b487187439c0b61d66165d8e8bf" type="folder">OV 4-7</container></did><bioghist id="aspace_de8d993f0163669ae5ac3fa967d38fe6"><head>Historical Note - Gmeeoorh</head><p><title>Gmeeoorh</title> was written in 1974 and was intended to premiere at the 1974 International Contemporary Organ Music Festival. However, it was cancelled due to lack of time to prepare (See Hartt School Collection (ARCH062), "International Contemporary Organ Music Festival" file for more details). <title>Gmeeoorh</title> premiered on February 24, 1975 at the South Church in New Britain and was performed by Clyde Holloway. Holloway later performed the piece again at the 1975 International Contemporary Organ Music Festival in June.</p></bioghist><scopecontent id="aspace_cc63bddc2e9cc7183d81aeffb4f4ff67"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>This files consists primarily of printed music and scores, and in some cases synopses, texts, and instructions, for the following:
Organ Music by Felix Werder (1963, 1973); <title>Gmeeoorh</title> by Iannis Xenakis (1974); <title>The Wound-Dresser, Melodrama, After Walt Whitman</title> by Rudy Shakelford (Circa 1975- circa 1976); <title>Chrysalis</title> by Vincent Plush (1978); <title>Opus 231</title> by Ernst Krenek (1900, printed with annotations 1979); <title>Toccata I</title> and <title>Toccatta II</title> by Klaus Hashagen (1979); Selections from the National Convention of the American Guild of Organists (from June 1982 Meeting); <title>Sonata in Two Movements and Epilogue</title> by Sven-Erik Back (1983); <title>Toccata e Corale Boleslaw Woytowicz in Memoriam</title> by Witold Szalonek (1988); <title>Encompassing: for Two Organists</title> by Vincent Plush (undated); and some unidentified organ music (undated).</p><p>Many of these pieces were commissioned for the Institute of Contemporary Organ Music and/or dedicated to John Holtz.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_ee604194a5b333ab17b960bb5dfa2e34" level="file"><did><unittitle>Programs</unittitle><unitdate normal="1968/1985" type="inclusive">1968-1985</unitdate><container altrender="document box legal (D15105)" id="aspace_74a5a5a5dc650bcd02fc9f515e57fa5e" label="Mixed Materials [0207303179916]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_fe4fdc76d00d1393c7d535d1f771e8ca" parent="aspace_74a5a5a5dc650bcd02fc9f515e57fa5e" type="folder">10-12</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_c67242f9fa4078a5b29d9a3e6b8d9c51" level="file"><did><unittitle>Scrapbooks</unittitle><physdesc altrender="whole"><extent altrender="materialtype spaceoccupied">2 Volumes</extent></physdesc><unitdate normal="1971/1979" type="inclusive">1971-1979</unitdate><container altrender="document box legal (D15105)" id="aspace_3bf2e20fcb358e85a85249e858b6ae78" label="Mixed Materials [0207303179916]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_87d28420a1dd95b8f9f379174742f5e2" parent="aspace_3bf2e20fcb358e85a85249e858b6ae78" type="folder">13</container><container altr